{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <div class ="wrapper">
    <main class="container my-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

        <section class="faq mt-5">
            <h2>General Questions</h2>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>1. How can I book a space travel experience?</h3>
                <p>To book a space travel experience, please visit our "Bookings" page and follow the step-by-step instructions provided.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>2. What are the eligibility criteria for space travel?</h3>
                <p>Eligibility criteria vary depending on the type of space travel experience. Please check the specific requirements listed on each destination's page.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="faq mt-5">
            <h2>Destinations</h2>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>3. How can I choose a destination for my space journey?</h3>
                <p>You can explore our range of destinations on the "Destinations" page. Each destination offers a unique experience, so choose the one that interests you the most.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>4. Can I visit multiple destinations in one trip?</h3>
                <p>Multi-destination trips may be available for certain packages. Please contact our customer support for more information.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="faq mt-5">
            <h2>Booking and Payment</h2>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>5. What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
                <p>We accept major credit cards, PayPal, and bank transfers for booking payments.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <h3>6. Is a deposit required when booking?</h3>
                <p>Yes, a deposit is typically required to secure your booking. The deposit amount varies depending on the chosen package.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    </div>
{% endblock %}
